The Crystal Dunes  is a region in nothern [[Eudin|The Kingdom of Eudin]] known for is shining dunes of snow.  It extends from the northern shore of Eudin down to the northern edge of [[Blackwood Forest]]. The area is known to be difficult to live in, having earned the nickname 'The Crystal Wastes' or 'The White Wastes'. Locals to the region generally take exception to this nickname, saying that it is dissmissive to what they have built. The area is fairly sparsely populated, with most of the inhabitants clustered in the larger settlements.